# 🔵 FastAPI Backend Explained

---

## 📌 Overview

This backend is built using Python and FastAPI.

---

## ⚙️ Features

- High performance  
- Automatic validation  
- Built-in documentation  

---

## 📄 Swagger Docs

Available at:
http://localhost:8000/docs

---

## 🗄️ Database

Uses SQLite with Python sqlite3 module.

---

## 🔗 Routes

### GET /api/students
Get all students

### POST /api/students
Add new student

### DELETE /api/students/{id}
Delete student

---

## 🧠 Key Concepts

- Decorators define routes  
- JSON responses are automatic  
- Clean and structured API design  

---

## 🎯 Summary

FastAPI simplifies API development with speed and built-in features.
